    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "The snap neovim works great. But, it'd be awesome if we could have separate configs for the traditional and the snap package. To do that, we need to specify the `XDG_CONFIG_HOME` and `XDG_DATA_DIR`. We can also add a migrate helper. Thus, the current user will also not suffer.",
